=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818660/extras/91a49f09e6ecd68c9d1672d8a7a13c11.mp4?t=1722254202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Combine strategic planning and improvisation to clear out hordes of mini middle managers. Each run is randomly generated, creating unique challenges and strategies in each playthrough. Figure out how to eliminate waves of weird little guys while enduring the chaos you’ve created. Upgrade towers and purchase powerful items with gathered cash.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't Forget the Hats!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818660/extras/58fa81e566d6b234d78e00f3ae6acbc6.avif?t=1722254202\" width=624 height=168 /></span><br>Unlock a variety of headwear, each with its own unique effect on gameplay. We will not go into further detail. Just know that there are hats.",
